org.elasticsearch.action.count

Class CountRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.elasticsearch.common.ContextHolder

              • org.elasticsearch.action.count.CountRequest
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IndicesRequest, IndicesRequest.Replaceable, Streamable

    public class CountRequest
extends BroadcastOperationRequest<CountRequest>
    A request to count the number of documents matching a specific query. Best created with Requests.countRequest(String...).

    The request requires the query source to be set either using source(QuerySourceBuilder), or source(byte[]).

    See Also:
    CountResponse, Client.count(CountRequest), Requests.countRequest(String...)
